commentTextItems.html: outside the off stump. Comes forward and defends

commentPostTextItems.html: And once again its Shahzad and Nawroz , who guide Afghanistan to victory and Cooper's effort earlier in the day goes in vain as the bowlers did not do a good job of defending the total. Fielders did not support them too as they dropped couple of catches offered by Shahzad. So now Scotland v Afghanistan becomes a virtual semi-final. Join us day after for that match

milestones.description: Karim Sadiq and Shahzad's 86-run partnership is AFG's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 53 between Mohammad Nabi and Nawroz Mangal
Nawroz Mangal and Asghar Afghan's 93-run partnership is AFG's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 39 between Mohammad Nabi and Nawroz Mangal
Samiullah Shinwari has become the top wicket-taker for AFG in ODIs with 14 wickets, going past Hamid Hassan's 12
Asghar Afghan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for AFG, going past Mohammad Nabi
